body:

whether I need to configure environment variables ?

Hi, I faced the same error. Maybe you've made some progress on it?

> 

Do you run it from core/bin/prover folder ?
I tried but then it ends up with this error: "error[E0422]: cannot find struct, variant or union type `LineColumn` in crate `proc_macro`"

> I tried but then it ends up with this error: "error[E0422]: cannot find struct, variant or union type `LineColumn` in crate `proc_macro`"

So, I am trying to fix some errors too (error: to use a constant of type `TypeId` in a pattern, `TypeId` must be annotated with `#[derive(PartialEq, Eq)]`
) .

But it fixes error that post's author has.

> I tried but then it ends up with this error: "error[E0422]: cannot find struct, variant or union type `LineColumn` in crate `proc_macro`"

cargo update -p proc-macro2@1.0.52
thanks! Now i have the same error as you mentioned above

> thanks! Now i have the same error as you mentioned above

Please send some your WhatsApp or Telegram to this [mail]( logunov.dennis@gmail.com), because I don't want to spam here)
